OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,FITV Border's political correspondent
OL,7,FTom Shedrick has the latest on the
OL,8,Finquiry.
OL,10,FA victim of the says contracting
OL,11,FHepatitis C has been "a huge plight of
OL,12,Flife" after he was infected with
OL,13,Fcontaminated blood in 1986.
OL,15,FBill Wright, from Dumfries, was also
OL,16,Fsubsequently registered with
OL,17,Fhemophilia and now lives with liver
OL,18,Fcirrhosis.
