OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,FHe has been one of the lead
OL,7,Fcampaigners calling for fair and
OL,8,Ffaster compensation for those affected
OL,9,Fby the scandal, and has also been the
OL,10,FChair of Hemophilia Scotland since it
OL,11,Fwas founded in 2012.
OL,13,FHe said: "As the chairman of a
OL,14,Fcharity, I've sat in the front rooms
OL,15,Fof so many people who have been
OL,16,Faffected.
OL,18,F"Many many people have frankly lost
OL,19,Floved ones as a consequence of being
OL,20,Finfected with either hepatitis C or
OL,21,FHIV.
