OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,F"Those stories are really brutal and
OL,7,Fthe impacts have been life changing."
OL,9,FProtestors gathered on Abbington Green
OL,10,Foutside parliament on Wednesday to
OL,11,Frally MPs and put pressure on the
OL,12,Fgovernment to ensure victims of the
OL,13,Fscandal get the compensation they
OL,14,Fdeserve.
OL,16,F"We're looking to achieve two things
OL,17,Ftoday," Mr Wright said.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
