OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,F"The budget is of course taking place
OL,7,Fnext week, we want the government to
OL,8,Fmake sure that they allocate
OL,9,Fsufficient funds in order to pay
OL,10,Fcompensation to everyone who's been
OL,11,Faffected and infected by the disaster.
OL,13,F"The second point is, we really need
OL,14,Fgovernment to be much more transparent
OL,15,Fin terms of what it's actually doing
OL,16,Fto make the arrangements to make those
OL,17,Fcompensation payments."
