OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,FHe continued: "Until now, they've been
OL,7,Fpretty secretive, albeit they're
OL,8,Fclaiming that they're working very
OL,9,Fhard - we've seen no detail of that
OL,10,Fwhatsoever.
OL,12,F"So we're down here to try and get
OL,13,Fsome answers and to try and ensure
OL,14,Fthat sufficient funds are allocated."
OL,16,FThe Infected Blood Inquiry made its
OL,17,Ffinal recommendations on compensation
OL,18,Ffor victims and their loved ones in
OL,19,FApril 2023.
