OL,6,FAlmost a year since they were
OL,7,Fpublished calling for a compensation
OL,8,Fbody to be up and running by the end
OL,9,Fof 2023, campaigners say the
OL,10,Fgovernment continues to drag its heels
OL,11,Fover committing to compensation
OL,12,Fpayments.
OL,14,F"In April last year, 10 months ago,
OL,15,FSir Brian Langstaff said arrangements
OL,16,Fshould start to be made now for
OL,17,Fcompensation," Mr Wright said.
