OL,3,CInfected blood victim says scandal has
OL,4,Cbeen 'a huge plight of life'
OL,6,F"He set out a detailed report of how
OL,7,Fthat compensation should be paid -
OL,8,Fthat an arms length body should be
OL,9,Festablished
OL,11,F"There's no word whatsoever about that
OL,12,Fbody being established.
OL,14,F"The whole point of it was that it
OL,15,Factually involved those who had been
OL,16,Faffected in order that we could work
OL,17,Fwith government to make suitable
OL,18,Farrangements."
